name: Whistle Bells
body:
### Hi! Welcome to my personal website.
I'll be updating this site pretty soon with tons of new content. In the meantime, this page is mainly under construction, but feel free to check around if you're just interested in checking out things.

```
COMING SOON: PROJECTS PAGE
```

I'm a student at Stuyvesant High School, I like math, and I hope to use this website as my personal playground and canvas.

### About Me
I love volunteering, programming, singing, and reading. I suppose I'm nerdy in some ways, as well.

### Favorite Things
Hmm...my favorite book is Ender's Game, my favorite movie is Big Hero 6, my favorite song is "On Top of the World" by Greek Fire, my favorite band is Paramore, and my favorite store is H&M. I also quite enjoy eating at Chipotle and Pinkberry.

### Authors
Sharon Lin (@sharon-lin) is fairly quirky and likes banana smoothies.

### Contact information
Haha, I'll figure this out later.
